The Government's Decisions:
Taking into account the salient points of the study committee report of the scheme "Gaon aadhi godowns."
To make the scheme a reality, the government has to draft a "village there godown" scheme.
The following committee is being constituted to make recommendations.
The Committee shall prepare a draft of the scheme and submit it to the Government within two months.
The decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra's www.maharashtra.gov.in website.
